Hi Martina,

Yes that could be your mozilla settings. Please see below.

- Click the menu button Menu and click Options.
- In the Options tab, select the Applications panel.
- In the Search field, type PDF to find the Portable Document Format (PDF) entry.


This article show how you can update your settings. https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/questions/1156348

Let us know if this helps? Cheers!

Hi Heath
